description:
Welcome to JSA's "Christ in Hymns, a Live Experience with JSA II"! We're excited to share this beautiful performance of some of our favorite hymns, sung with passion and reverence to our Lord. We would like to thank those who suggested hymns for this episode. At JSA, our mission is to spread the message of love, hope, and faith in our Lord Jesus Christ through our music ministry. Hymns have a unique power to connect us with our spiritual roots and bring us closer to God. You'll hear beloved hymns such as "Speak to my soul," "showers of blessings," "turn your eyes upon," and more. We hope this episode inspires and blesses you. As a ministry, we rely on your support to continue creating music that touches hearts and souls.
